The 2018 Billboards Music Awards held at the MGM Grand Garden Arena in Las Vegas yesterday, May 20. The awards which had defining moments became the first awards show to be broadcast on NBC. Hosted by Kelly Clarkson, we witnessed beautiful performances from Demi Lovato, Shawn Mendes, Ariana Grande, the legendary Janet Jackson among others. Of all the nominees, Ed Sheeran, Bruno Mars and Kendrick Lamar got the highest nominations (15) including Top Artist category. Next in line was Post Malone with 13 and Imagine Dragons with 11 nominations. Here is the complete list of winners: Drake
